# Mind's Eye Theatre Revised – Book List

## Core Rulebooks

- **Laws of the Night Revised Edition** (WW5013) – The primary rulebook. ☑
- **Laws of the Night Revised Edition (Limited)** (WW5015) – Deluxe version with extra art. ☐

## Primary Supplements

- **Laws of the Night: Camarilla Guide** (WW5017) – Rules for Camarilla-specific clans and positions. ☑
- **Laws of the Night: Sabbat Guide** (WW5018) – Rules for Sabbat ritae and packs. ☑
- **Laws of the Night: Storytellers Guide** (WW5021) – Advice and advanced mechanics for game masters. ☑
- **Laws of the Night: Anarch Guide** (WW5040) – Rules for the Anarch movement. ☑

## Specialized & Cross-Compatible Books

- **Laws of Elysium** (WW5011) – Rules for elder vampires; while pre-dating Revised, it is largely compatible. ☑
- **Liber des Ghouls: The Book of Ghouls** (WW5006) – Rules for playing mortal servants. ☑
- **Faith and Fire** (WW5038) – Dark Ages: Vampire LARP rules (often used for historical flashbacks). ☑
- **Vampire by Gaslight** (WW5041) – Victorian-era settings for Vampire LARP. ☐
- **Laws of the East** (WW5016) – Rules for playing Kindred of the East in LARP. ☑

## Play Aids & Media

- **Mind's Eye Theatre Journal** (Issues 1–8) – Magazine featuring official errata and new rules. ☑
- **Mind's Eye Theatre Discipline Deck** – Reference cards for vampire powers. ☑
- **Mind's Eye Theatre Discipline Deck 2** – Additional reference cards for advanced or sect powers. ☐
- **Mind's Eye Theatre Gift Deck** – Reference cards for Garou gifts. ☑
- **Mind's Eye Theatre Prop Deck** – Reference cards for props and handouts. ☑

## Werewolf: The Apocalypse (Revised Era)

- **Laws of the Wild Revised Edition** (WW5024) – Core rules for Garou LARP. ☑
- **Laws of the Wild: Changing Breeds 1** (WW5031) – Rules for Bastet, Nuwisha, Ratkin, and Gurahl. ☐
- **Laws of the Wild: Changing Breeds 2** (WW5034) – Rules for Corax, Mokole, Nagah, and Rokea. ☐
- **Book of the Wyrm** (WW5027) – Rules for Fomorians and Black Spiral Dancers. ☑

## Mage, Changeling, & Wraith

- **Laws of Ascension** (WW5029) – Core rules for Mage: The Ascension. ☑
- **Laws of Ascension: Companion** (WW5035) – Expanded rules for Technocracy and Traditions. ☑
- **The Shining Host Player's Guide** (WW5023) – The Revised-era update for Changeling: The Dreaming. ☑
- **Oblivion** (WW5004) – The primary book for Wraith: The Oblivion. (Note: This pre-dates the 1999 Revised launch but remained the standard throughout the era). ☑

## Hunters, Mummies, & The End

- **Laws of the Reckoning** (WW5033) – Rules for playing Imbued Hunters. ☑
- **Laws of Resurrection** (WW5039) – Rules for playing Mummies. ☑
- **Laws of the Hunt Revised** (WW5025) – Rules for mortal investigators and hedge magic. ☑
- **Laws of Judgment** (WW5042) – The "Time of Judgment" book for ending LARP chronicles. ☑
